{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"29":" Chapters on Food"},"section_detail":{"29":{"hadithnumber_first":3251,"hadithnumber_last":3370,"arabicnumber_first":3251,"arabicnumber_last":3370}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3306,"arabicnumber":3306,"text":"Rapporté par Abu Darda’ : Le Messager d'Allah ﷺ ne refusait jamais une invitation à manger de la viande, et il acceptait toujours la viande qu'on lui offrait en cadeau","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Very Daif"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Very Daif"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Very Daif"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Daif"}],"reference":{"book":29,"hadith":56}}]}